
<header id="header">
	<div class="inner text-center">
		<a href="/main/mypage" class="image avatar"><img src="/assets/logo.jpg" alt="" /></a>
		<h1><strong>CowGroup!!</strong></h1>
		<p>자신만의 소그룹을 만들어 얘기해봅시다.</p>
		<a href="/main/create" class="button">소그룹생성하기</a><br><br>
		<a href="/main/mypage" class="button">돌아가기</a>
	</div>
</header>


<div id="main">
    
        <section>
		    <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1em;">검색된 소모임</h2>
			<div class="row">
				<% if @list.empty? %>
				검색된 소모임이 없습니다.
				<% else %>
			    <% @list.each do |l| %>
			    <div class="col-sm-6">
				<article class="6u 12u$(xsmall) work-item">
					<a href="/main/view/<%= l.id %>" class="image fit thumb"><img src="/assets/lion.png" alt="" /></a>
					<center><h3><%= l.gp_name %></h3>
					<p><%= l.creater %></p></center>
				</article>
				</div>
				<% end %>
				<% end %>
			</div>
		</section>
</div>


